@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .

### Alice isSiblingOf Bob, and the property is symmetric -> Bob isSiblingOf Alice.
:SymmetricProperty_Bob :symmetricIsSiblingOf :SymmetricProperty_Alice .
